$ VB Editor: Tools -> Options -> General (tab)

Form Grid Settings:
  • Show grid
  • Grid units (widht/height)
  • Align controls to grid

Other
  • Show tool tips
  • Collapse project hides windows

Edit and Continue
  • Notiy before state loss
 
Error Trapping
  • Break on all errors, or
  • Break in class module, or
  • Break on unandled errors

Compile
  • Compile on demand
  • And if so: Background compilation
